main event: An unidentified flying object was observed for about 15 minutes, initially appearing round but later taking an oblong shape.
interesting points: The object was encased in a silver-gray colored shell., No sound was heard during the observation., It moved from east to west at a slow speed., The object disappeared abruptly., The report suggests that the object might be some type of balloon.
witness description: The report reflects personal judgement and opinion of the reporting individual.
